<img src="./resources/images/headlines/khp_alpha.png" style="position: absolute; left: 10%; top: 15%; width: 80%; z-index: ;"/>

???
- the court case wasn't against minority drivers, it was out-of-state drivers,
  but the ideas are the same

---
<img src="./resources/images/ms_base.png" style="position: absolute; left: 2.5%; top: 12.5%; width: 100%; z-index: ;"/>
???
- i'll keep referring to minority and white civilians just keep consistent
