<img src="./resources/images/klm_relax_1.png" style="position: absolute; left: 0%; top: 0%; width: 100%; z-index: ;"/>
???
- but now that we have an algorith to help, we can extend the original analysis
- for example, some critics pushed back on the assumption that force might be
  used less in discretionary stops
- it's impractical to re-derive the results, but now there's an algorithm to
  help with the deduction, all it takes is another 10 seconds

